 Write a program that will tell whether the given number is divisible by 3 & 6.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------number=int(input("enter the numer:"))
if number%3==0 and number%6==0:
    print("The given number is divisible by both 3 and 6.")
else:
    print("The given number is not divisible by both 3 and 6.")

output:
enter the numer: 6
The given number is divisible by both 3 and 6.
